description: Cliff Jensen and Ashton McKay are out tossing a ball when Beaux Banks spots them and wants to toss more than a ball with Ashton. When Cliff steps away for a minute, Beaux swoops in to offer Ashton a private massage. Ashton happily agrees and Beaux gives him more than he bargained for. Not one to be left out, Cliff makes sure he gets a turn as well.
title: Couples Massage Part 2
